We subsequently identified the maximal nontoxic dose of each MNV-1 PPMO in cytotoxicity assays. All the PPMOs designed for this study (Table 1
and Fig. 1) were nontoxic up to a concentration of 20 μM (Fig. 2
). Higher concentrations of most PPMOs induced cytotoxicity, with the exception of PPMOs A and C, which remained nontoxic even at concentrations of 80 μM.
